Examples

>>> print(format("select a, b from t"))
SELECT
    a,
    b
FROM
    t

>>> print(format("select sum(a) over (partition by b), count(b) from t group by c"))
SELECT
    sum(a) over (partition by b),
    count(b)
FROM
    t
GROUP BY
    c
